I would like an option to "E-mail this issue" on the left side "Operations" Menu. Although I have set up notifications to notify assignees.. sometimes it would be nice to just advise a user of an issue with one click (and then e-mail to user/group).

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-5954].
  {panel}

Currently, after the POPService has processed an email and created an issue/comment from it, it deletes the mail.  It would be useful if JIRA could skip processed mails rather than deleting them.

This would then allow JIRA to be used as a passive recorder of the contents of a POP box, which humans are responsible for managing.  Passive support tracking would often be preferable to the current intrusive tracking; for instance, it wouldn't lose the Cc list.

